Wednesday, August 24, 1994

MERIT DOCKET

94-989. Cope v. DeSanto.

In Habeas Corpus. On motion to dismiss by William H. Dallman, motion to dismiss by Robert P. DeSanto et al., and motion to amend petition. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
